text: @FedEx My friend across the pond @meganskulski bought a gift, paid with PayPal, and it was assigned to the default address - an old one in Fayetteville. She immediately called Fedex THREE times, 2 people said that the package can be rerouted when the tracking number arrived.

@FedEx Tracking number arrived, so Meg called at 4am - they said nothing they can do! She's associated with military - is this how you treat military who have to constantly move? This is a gift for her mother and now it's either gonna be late - or stolen!
@DanielJFalconer Hello Daniel, this is Andrew. I am sorry to hear your friend is experiencing these issues. She can reach out to us at @FedExHelp and we would be happy to help her if we can.
@FedExHelp Thank youy, Andrew. @meganskulski Here you go, Meg.
